keyFacts: The document is a Google subscriber information record for an account with username 'gmaxl'.
The account was created on April 12, 2015, and shows login activity through October 2016.
The account had access to numerous Google services including Gmail, Google Drive, Google Calendar, Google Voice, and YouTube.
The document is marked as 'Google Confidential and Proprietary' and appears in the Epstein case document release (EFTA00091936).
